I've got special permission to change the config file.
The config files for the 3 sensors will be
"keySensor,motionSensor and doorSensor" instead of just sensor.

Message Formats

Everything to gateway (even backend?)
-------------------------------------
register
	Type:register;Action:clock-deviceType-ip-port
currValue
	Type:currValue;Action:clock-state


Front Gate to Back Gate
-------------------------
log
	Type:log;Action:deviceValue-deviceType-state-clock-ip-port


Gateway to doorSensor
-------------------------
poll
	Type:currState;Action:poll;

Gateway to Device
-------------------------
switch
	Type:switch;Action:on;


Key ToDos (personal questions)
---------------
Central Synchronization vs Distributed Synchronization
Clocks (actual time vs process time)